---
title: Chicken Tikka Naan Pizza with Sweet Potato Fries and Mango Chutney
description: We’ve combined two of our customers’ favourite cuisines, Italian and Indian, to create a winning recipe for your next pizza night. Introducing the third recipe from our limited edition “Street Food” collection: Chicken Tikka “Pizza”. We’ve used fresh naan breads for the base of these delicious pizzas, topping them with a tikka spiced tomato sauce, succulent chicken pieces, roasted red peppers and mozzarella. Serve the pizzas up with the sweet potato fries and dressed salad and dive in. The perfect ‘tear and share’ for a night in with friends!
